Package tools

Comprises the main components of MUSIAL, i.e. each class implements the procedure for a major step in the MUSIAL analysis-pipeline.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ArgumentsParser
    Parser for command line arguments.
    InputPreprocessor
    Comprises static methods to generate sets of ReferenceAnalysisEntry and SampleAnalysisEntry instances.
    OutputWriter
    Comprises a static method to generate all output files.
    SampleAnalyser
    Comprises static methods to analyze samples.
    SnpEffAnnotator
    Runs local installation of SnpEff via command line.
